### TITLE ###
Gutter width accounts for context lines
### DESCRIPTION ###
When a label is on a single-digit line (e.g. line 9) but context lines extend
into double digits (line 10+), the gutter must be wide enough for all displayed
lines so that the | pipes stay vertically aligned.
